<div class="w75 right"><img width="75" height="75" border="0" alt="Dewey &amp; LeBoeuf Accounting Fraud Case Goes to Jury" src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2015/09/17/business/17DB-DEWEY/17DB-DEWEY-square320.jpg"/></div>
